    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six. This specimen features a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and the M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure optimal valve timing. The individual throttle bodies provide the signature induction note and sharp throttle response enthusiasts crave. The suspension maintains factory-spec damping and lateral rigidity, while the braking system shows consistent bite without fade. A driver-focused example that balances performance integrity with honest cosmetic patina.",
